COMMITTEE AMENDMENT

COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 325, L.D. 496
1 SUMMARY
22 This amendment, which is the majority report of the committee, replaces the bill and
33 changes the title. The amendment requires that Silver Alerts be issued to all hospitals and
44 homeless shelters in the State and to a statewide association of libraries.
